---
title: HelloHero: Double Salt & Pepper Chicken with Garlic Rice, Honey-Soy Veggies & Japanese Mayo
description: Watch out salt and pepper squid, because our chicken version is going to steal even your biggest fans! With all the spicy flavour, but pan-fried instead of deep-fried, this is a quick and easy dinner that's going to blow your mind.

*We’ve replaced the crispy shallots in this recipe with coriander
due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
